<emphasis box="[199,352,618,643]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" reason="1">Distribution.</emphasis>
—
</emphasis>
Hispaniola, 
<collectingCountry box="[515,651,618,642]" name="Puerto Rico" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
, their satellite islands, and 
