Culebra (
<figureCitation box="[1105,1188,618,642]" captionStart="FIGURE 15" captionStartId="28.[151,250,1449,1472]" captionTargetBox="[169,1413,622,1412]" captionTargetId="figure-364@28.[139,1438,591,1465]" captionTargetPageId="28" captionText="FIGURE 15. Distribution of the Xiphosurus chamaeleonides and Xiphosurus cuvieri Species Groups." pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
